Uses of Package
model

  • Packages that use model 
    Package Description
    application
    Package 'application' contains the entry point Main for GS_L and a non-commented application.css
    model
    Package model contains 3 classes: Facet encapsulates each constituent component of an assessment. Nest encapsulates the various parameters of the assessment design. SampleSizeTree encapsulates the sample sizes and their relationships.
    steps
    package steps contains 3 classes providing the major functionality of GS_L.
    utilities
    package utilities contains 11 utility classes adding specific functionality.
